I had problems in my missions last evening as well.  They did seme harder to me.  Evens were beating the tar outta me I had to zone more than once.<br>
<br>
As to the weapons I am lvl 18 and my weapons are QL20.  Most of my armor is also close to my level or above.  So I am wondering what the heck happen.  Did they increase the difficulties of the mobs. They did seem to have some massive Hitpoints.  I used 3 times the amount of ammo on them than I normally have too. (almost ran out).<br>
